Revision history for Games-Simutrans-Pakset

0.02  2021-06-02 08:21:46 EDT
        - The path parameter may be passed to new().
        - Language 'en' is assumed when none is given even when no
          system environment variables exist (e.g., Win, FreeBSD)
        - Images with a subscript of '[-]' are parsed and saved.
        - A remnant bareword filehandle was replaced with modern code.

0.01  2021-05-28 20:59:06 EDT
        - Initial release
